    <h2>Privacy and Data Protection</h2>
    <p>We respect your privacy and protect your personal information in accordance with applicable laws. Data collected is used solely for:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Providing and improving our services</li>
      <li>Communicating with you about projects</li>
      <li>Complying with legal obligations</li>
      <li>Website analytics for experience improvements</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Changes to These Terms</h2>
    <p>We may update these Terms. Continued use after changes means acceptance of the revised Terms.</p>

    <h2>Applicable Law</h2>
    <p>These Terms are governed by the laws of the State of Florida.</p>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>Questions about these Terms? Contact us:</p>
    <p><strong>Paramount Property Restoration</strong><br />
    Phone: (786) 602-2217<br />
    Service area: Florida</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>